metadata.name: Osprey's breakfast
metadata.description:
I've followed this Osprey's habits for a few months. I am not gonna lie, the first attempts were really frustrating, but patience is a sweet companion. 

I am pretty sure she heard me scream in awe when I saw the shot in my camera's display, because she did a few circles around me, with her freshly captured breakfast before taking off.

**A high quality print will go to the proud owner of this piece**.
